snippet.title: Goblins & Grottos Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Goblin Portal & Psychic Software are today announcing that Goblins and Grottos, the 2D comedy puzzle-platformer will fully launch on July 7th with all new features, maps and more. 

Get the game at steam: 
http://store.steampowered.com/app/389190/

http://www.goblinsandgrottos.com
